      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients that are expected to receive VATS segmenectomy or lobectomy regardless of
             disease entity

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  not done by VATS anatomical resection

          -  patient does not agree to the study

          -  postoperative hospital stay exceeds 7 days due to postoperative complications

          -  existence of preoperative renal insufficiency (Cr &gt; 1.5)

          -  OT/PT &gt; 120

          -  history of Lidocaine hypersensitivity
      </textblock>
